subject: Tennis
World War I (1914-18)
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: In the 100th anniversary year of the height of her once-famous ancestor’s career, Anna Wilding stumbled upon a riddle that has turned her pursuit of knowledge into a cry for fairness.
